title: HelloHero: Peppercorn Lamb Rump with Veggie Fries & Cucumber Salad
description: You know you’re in for a good night when the only thing standing between you and this classy lamb dish is a matter of minutes. With only the most tender lamb rump cut, a punchy pepper crusting and baked veggie fries, you just can't go wrong.

